      "text": [
        "4907 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: \"مَلْعُونٌ مَلْعُونٌ مَنْ ضَيَّعَ مَنْ يَعُولُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4907 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Cursed, cursed is the one who neglects those under his care.\""
        ]
      }
